title: unix: doesn't build
body:
What does 'go version' print?
go version devel +d4904f349bc8 Sat Oct 04 08:09:39 2014 +1000 linux/amd64

What steps reproduce the problem?
1. go get -u -v code.google.com/p/go.sys/unix

What happened?
# code.google.com/p/go.sys/unix
../../../code.google.com/p/go.sys/unix/zsyscall_linux_amd64.go:672: undefined: syscall
../../../code.google.com/p/go.sys/unix/zsyscall_linux_amd64.go:1133: undefined: syscall

What should have happened instead?
Successfully get and install.

Please provide any additional information below.
